===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|music}} An [[electronic]] [[instrument]] that creates its [[sound]]s with electronics and has a [[keyboard]].
# {{lb|en|music}} An electronic instrument [[module]] that creates its sounds with electronics and does not have any keyboard.
# {{lb|en|electronics}} An electronic [[circuit]] that generates an electronic [[signal]] [[oscillation]] with [[accurate]] [[timing]] from a [[reference]] [[oscillator]].
# {{lb|en|electronics}} An electronic [[device]] that generates electronic signal [[pattern]]s to [[test]] an electronic circuit.

